OL,3,CMurder arrest after death of 74-year-
OL,4,Cold man
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder after the death of a 74-year-
OL,8,Fold man.
OL,10,FGwent Police said officers attended a
OL,11,Fproperty in Bythway Road, Trevethin,
OL,12,FTorfaen on Thursday afternoon, after
OL,13,Freports of a man suffering serious
OL,14,Finjuries.
OL,16,FThe man has been named as Nicholas
OL,17,F"Brian" Parfitt. He pronounced dead at
OL,18,Fthe scene.
